metadata.name: Hizzy's Red BeSomeone #1/250
metadata.description: BeSomeone Red Graffiti - The Be Someone Slogan First Appeared on the RR Bridge Over I-45 in September of 2012. Since Then it Has Been Covered Over, Re-Done and Has Become A Piece of Houston History. The Artist Who is Known To Some, Can Never "Officially" Take Credit. The Red Version First Appeared in Late March 2023. I Took These Photos with My Nikon Z6II with a 50mm F1.8 Lens.
